<span id="freeTextContainer10255033540462174865">I don&apos;t even know where to begin! First, I was completely blown away by this book in the best possible way! It&apos;s very difficult to write this review without spoilers, but it will be spoiler free! To say that unexpected things happen would not be at all surprising for this series. Lucian&apos;s stories have never been predictable. He has already introduced us to some pretty bizarre characters with some very unique features and talents in the prior Ruin books. This story has even more Lucian-spawned pa</span>
  <span id="freeText10255033540462174865" style="display:none">I don't even know where to begin! First, I was completely blown away by this book in the best possible way! It's very difficult to write this review without spoilers, but it will be spoiler free! To say that unexpected things happen would not be at all surprising for this series. Lucian's stories have never been predictable. He has already introduced us to some pretty bizarre characters with some very unique features and talents in the prior Ruin books. This story has even more Lucian-spawned paranormal freaks colliding into Ruin's world and creating chaos for he and Isadore. I don't want to give away details of the storyline, but I can say that this book totally rocked my emotions, then grabbed hold of my senses, and I could not put it down until I read the very last page. But it was not the end. Oh no, the stage is set for more mind blowing events and masterful story telling by the truly gifted wordsmith, Mr. Bane.</span>
