  <span id="freeText4013725093638357291" style="display:none">Wow!!! This series has been one page-turner after another! "Ruin: The Turning" continues to push the boundaries with its otherworldly battle to fulfill the prophecy. Ruin's will is tested time and again, as he's taken to the edge of darkness and beyond. Nothing is as it seems, and this next installment is one surprising scene after another that will steal your breath over and over. The battle of angels, demons and other beings is fantastical and thrilling, and the cliffhanger ending completely caught me by surprise. I loved the descriptive scenes! The powerful dialogue was at times gripping, while other times the snarky humor gave it the perfect blend of comedic relief that leads to uneasy laughter. This series is a must read for those who want a good paranormal adventure!</span>
