  <span id="freeText3065270400571033868" style="display:none">A special link between a husband and a wife, just how far would you go to protect it?<br /><br />The beautiful writing style of Lucian Bane is set to draw you in to the story, a story where you are left questioning everything. Thick with twists and turns, colourful characters and vivid imagery. With shocks around every corner.<br /><br />As the story unfolds further we follow the star crossed lovers Isadore and Ruin on their epic journey as Ruin is forced to undertake his most conflicting assignment yet. We are introduced to new characters as they try to comprehend their roles in the greater story. RUIN: The Turning is packed with action and passion as we watch Ruin fight for the woman he loves and at the end......leaving us hungry for more.</span>
