    <a title="Ria Alexander  - Reading Is Our Satisfaction" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction"><img alt="Ria Alexander  - Reading Is Our Satisfaction" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1522465127p2/14748726.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1627519388?book_show_action=true">May 02, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ria Alexander  - Reading Is Our Satisfaction" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ria Alexander  - Reading Is Our Satisfaction" href="/user/show/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction">Ria Alexander  - Reading Is Our Satisfaction</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=best-indie-author">best-indie-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=fantasy-romance">fantasy-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=paranormal-romance">paranormal-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=indie-paranormal-romance">indie-paranormal-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=series">series</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=paranormal">paranormal</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=best-paranormal-romance">best-paranormal-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/14748726-ria-alexander---reading-is-our-satisfaction?shelf=erotica">erotica</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1627519388" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11663034094705574185">Where on earth do I begin???<br/>WOW!!!!! To say that this book was brilliant is an understatement!!!<br/>Lucian pours everything into it and leaves the reader still wantng more, if that&apos;s possible.<br/>He throws the proverbial &apos;kitchen sink&apos; at Ruin and Isadore, causing havoc and chaos everywhere.<br/>To say much more would be to give away the story....but let me just say here that Lucian you left me totally shocked.<br/>I want more...please give us more....<br/>There is so many paths that this story can take and I am excit</span>
  <span id="freeText11663034094705574185" style="display:none">Where on earth do I begin???<br />WOW!!!!! To say that this book was brilliant is an understatement!!!<br />Lucian pours everything into it and leaves the reader still wantng more, if that's possible.<br />He throws the proverbial 'kitchen sink' at Ruin and Isadore, causing havoc and chaos everywhere.<br />To say much more would be to give away the story....but let me just say here that Lucian you left me totally shocked.<br />I want more...please give us more....<br />There is so many paths that this story can take and I am excited to see which one you will take.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11663034094705574185" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


