<span id="freeTextContainer5217999009886947641">Well after just finishing the Ruin box set of the first 3 books I couldn&apos;t wait to read this one, but OMG what a roller coaster of a ride!! The storyline takes many twists and turns and didn&apos;t end up going where I thought it would, throwing my emotions all over the place!! We meet a couple of new characters in this book seem to have a major impact on what&apos;s going to happen next. Can&apos;t wait for the next book. Again this is a must read!!</span>
  <span id="freeText5217999009886947641" style="display:none">Well after just finishing the Ruin box set of the first 3 books I couldn't wait to read this one, but OMG what a roller coaster of a ride!! The storyline takes many twists and turns and didn't end up going where I thought it would, throwing my emotions all over the place!! We meet a couple of new characters in this book seem to have a major impact on what's going to happen next. Can't wait for the next book. Again this is a must read!!</span>
