<span id="freeTextContainer3606033141347041676"><strong>Better late than never</strong><br/><br/>I have just read all 4 RUIN books. There is an upside to being on the LATE Bane Train. I have now completed all of his works and I must say this was my favorite. It entailed All that makes a story great for me. Non Stop Action. Beautiful Seductive Love. Biting Sarcastic Humor between Lovers. And an ending that had me cursing at the author because I so badly didn&apos;t want it to be over! Oh I&apos;m in Book Hangover Heaven and I do not want the cure. </span>
