<span id="freeTextContainer6718685837665994799">I kept hoping it&apos;d get better, the editing would improve, someone would spell-check - but it didn&apos;t get happen. I figured by the time #4 rolled around I&apos;d have an understanding of who Ruin is and why he&apos;s here, be invested in the happy ending - but I&apos;m just not. I&apos;m merely disappointed and am putting the book away, without finishing it.<br/><br/>:(</span>
  <span id="freeText6718685837665994799" style="display:none">I kept hoping it'd get better, the editing would improve, someone would spell-check - but it didn't get happen. I figured by the time #4 rolled around I'd have an understanding of who Ruin is and why he's here, be invested in the happy ending - but I'm just not. I'm merely disappointed and am putting the book away, without finishing it.<br /><br />:(</span>
